reviewText: Did not have any information for women dealing with the addiction of alcohol and was not worth the price.

I purchased this video to review and possibly use it in the course of education material for  treatment and preventive instructional time. This video is wonderful and stresses the difference between men and women drinkers/alcoholics.

Blurb said A woman tracking her drinking for a month referenced to Morgan Freeman's "Supersize Me" There was nothing on the DVD that showed the cumlative effect of her drinking. VERY VERY disappointed. ABC News 20/20 Women and Alcohol
